## Decisions and Action Items

| Topic / Proposal | Dispatch Decision |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Caller ID Verification and Validation (CIDVV)** | Dispatched to the **STIR Working Group**, pending a potential charter update to accommodate the work. |
| **Email Verification Protocol (EVP)** | **Not dispatched to a WG.** The author was advised to continue discussions on the main email and DMARC mailing lists to build operator consensus. |
| **Email Security BCP / Applicability Statement** | Dispatched as **AD-sponsored** (or to a potential focused, short-lived WG), with the Area Directors to coordinate the appropriate path forward. |
| **PARCEP (Parental Controls)** | Dispatched to a **new, dedicated mailing list** to refine the architectural, security, and privacy implications. |
| **Taxonomy for Agentic AI Use Cases** | Dispatched to the **IRTF** (specifically targeting the NMRG) for exploratory research. |
| **Ciphertext Inference MCP** | Dispatched to **SECDISPATCH** (or **CFRG** for fundamental cryptographic review). |
| **Authorization Evidence for High-Risk Actions** | Dispatched to the **OAuth Working Group**. |

